data.description: Move right in to this beautiful, updated home in a central location.  The seller completely remodeled this home in 2021 inside and out to make it more efficient and handicap accessible. New windows, roof, appliances, bathrooms, LVP flooring, and ductless mini-split heating and air system. This better than new  home is completely insulated,  even the crawlspace that has a certificate from the professional contractor, and double pane windows to add to the efficiency and comfort. You'll be amazed at how inexpensive the utilities  and taxes are.  Feel completely secure with a brand new security system. Plumbing in place to add a shower to the second bath.
